PART 3: LEE-YANG ZEROS â€” COMPLEX ZEROS OF P_n(q)
  In statistical mechanics, the zeros of the partition function
  in the complex fugacity plane control phase transitions.
======================================================================

  n=3: P_3(q) has degree 3
    #0 real roots: []
    #1 conjugate pairs of complex roots
    Root moduli: [np.float64(1.7321), np.float64(1.7321)]

  n=4: P_4(q) has degree 5
