    #0 real roots: []
    #7 conjugate pairs of complex roots
    Root moduli: [np.float64(0.8231), np.float64(0.8231), np.float64(0.8231), np.float64(0.8231), np.float64(1.0092), np.float64(1.0092), np.float64(1.0092), np.float64(1.0092), np.float64(1.1781), np.float64(1.1781)]
    Modulus range: [0.8231, 1.4295]
    All on unit circle? False
    All on SOME circle? False

