PART 4: MOMENTS AND CUMULANTS OF H
  Under uniform distribution on tournaments
======================================================================

  n=3:
    Mean = 1.5000 (= n!/2^(n-1) = 1.5000)
    Variance = 0.7500
    Skewness = 1.1547
    Excess kurtosis = -0.6667
    Var/Mean = 0.5000
    Var/Mean^2 = 0.3333

  n=4:
    Mean = 3.0000 (= n!/2^(n-1) = 3.0000)
    Variance = 3.0000
    Skewness = 0.0000
